precis:
Amendment to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL REGULATIONS which
authorizes the Chairman to determine that, in matters involving an appeal
under the Excise Tax Act, only one member of the Tribunal constitutes a
quorum thereof.
